Package mazeGenerator

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MazeCreator
    This class represents the Strategy interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cell
    The class Cell is the basic entity a maze consists of.A cell represents one square field in the grid that later forms a maze.
    HelloLibrary
    This is a template class and can be used to start a new processing Library.
    HuntAndKill
    This class implements the Hunt and Kill algorithm for creating mazes.
    Kruskal
    This class implements the Kruskal algorithm for creating mazes.
    Maze
    Stores and manages entire mazes consisting of walls and cells.
    RecursiveBacktracker
    This class implements the Recursive Backtracking algorithm for creating mazes.
    RecursiveStrategy
    The class RecursiveStrategy provides the Template Methods for the classes Kruskal and RecursiveBacktracker.
    Wall
    This class represents the walls in the maze grid.
